    public class A5AlgebraRelation
extends BitSetAlgebraRelation<A5BaseRelation>
    The A5 Algebras of relations (see: Jérôme Euzenat, Algebras of ontology alignment relations, Proc. ISWC, 2008). JEPD relations between classes (based on set theory)
